<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٣٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٦٦٠٧ - عَنِ ابْنِ عُيَيْنَةَ، عَنْ يَحْيَى بْنِ سَعِيدٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ سَعِيدِ بْنِ الْمُسَيِّبِ قَالَ:</span> كَانَ عُمَرُ <span class="c2">«يَفْرِضُ لِلصَّبِيِّ إِذَا اسْتَهَلَ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>